title: Big Blue opens season with win over Regis, 154-97 (University of New England)
text: ( Source : University of New England ) Results BIDDEFORD, Maine -- Kayla Burgess led a balanced and deep University of New England women's swimming team with a pair of event wins as the Nor'easters defeated Regis College , 154-97, on Saturday
